text: Colobothea flavimacula is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Voet in 1806. It is known from South America.BioLib.cz - Colobothea flavimacula. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1806
title: Colobothea flavimacula
